Simple control programs for Caen N1470, written using the CAEN HV Wrapper Library.  Written for use in the UChicago photon lab to automate gain calibration of photomultiplier tubes.

The module can be controlled from the command line by the functions:

  ./getParameter param channels
  ./setParameter param channels


COMPILE INSTRUCTIONS:  download and install CAEN HV wrapper lib and place the header in ./include/.

* A modified branch of this code is in use at the FAST prototype experiment at the TA Black Rock Mesa site.
